description_data.value: ** RESERVED ** This candidate has been reserved by an organization or individual that will use it when announcing a new security problem. When the candidate has been publicized, the details for this candidate will be provided.

descriptions.value: SVR-116 firmware version 1.6.0.30028871 allows a remote authenticated attacker with an administrative privilege to execute arbitrary OS commands by sending a specially crafted request to the product.

La versión 1.6.0.30028871 del firmware SVR-116 permite a un atacante remoto autenticado con privilegios administrativos ejecutar comandos arbitrarios del sistema operativo enviando una solicitud especialmente manipulada al producto.
